Package: SLAP
Title: Scalable League Analytics Platform for R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Bailey", "Quinn", , "booequinn@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-5318-8310"))
Description: The NHL Scalable League Analytics Platform or SLAP is the framework for a pipeline that generates a processed database from procedurally scraping the NHL API. Generated SLAPbases are structured to be used for downstream analytics and can be dowloaded as a structured zip file. 
